{"tid":1421994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係你死，就係我地亡","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:20:40.000Z","uid":192358,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"189ab3ab0fce76abaf4efb5ea14b1c00360c0b30","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:29:55.000Z","msg":"琴日喺巴士聽到有個人講:<br />\n<br />\n去到而家呢個階段，好明顯將會有人喺衝突中被殺，一係就警察對示威者中出現，一係就藍絲或黑社會對示威者中出現，<br />\n一定要其中一方有人死至知驚，至可以俾到壓力政府，<br />\n你地想我地死先？定人地死先？<br />\n再係繼續而家咁搞，被捕示威者只會越來越多，<br />\n淋病無人敢搞，唯有搞popo，佢問大家點睇<br />\n<br />\n利申:和理非，反對任何暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27588202cf733de6dd5b11fbad043b7c941bf143","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:31:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4dcf7f7cd3f3834b54df8ed88b96b3501bf47f3","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72669a13f7a77f3d0a51f367cf8af1a8e9d9ebe7","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:33:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c2a53b936c5a2ed4e079e6f0a926a67ba2e37698","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78fdc430206a7713f22b6028ec8a6ff02380b7ff","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2e3693a66ae71b1a58e8b33fab02937047933027","tid":1421994,"uid":253833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:35:41.000Z","msg":"和理非新回合<br />\n［借acc][純建議] 8月24日 全港罷買日 搞「靜」香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1420749\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1420749</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"40b803600c63b1e74170799506b46f50d3e92056","tid":1421994,"uid":192358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:36:08.000Z","